## 5. Inventory (where hosts are listed)

```yaml
all:
  children:
    webservers:
      hosts:
        web1:
          ansible_host: 192.168.1.10
        web2:
          ansible_host: 192.168.1.11
```

**What this does** вҖ” defines two servers; the playbook can target **`webservers`**. **`ansible_host`** is the address Ansible uses for SSH.

