## 6. Roles вҖ” path you care about for OTel

```text
xotel_code/getafix/trunk/ansible/roles/otel-collector/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ tasks/main.yml
в”ңв”Җв”Җ handlers/main.yml
в”ңв”Җв”Җ defaults/main.yml
в””в”Җв”Җ templates/
    в””в”Җв”Җ otel-config.yaml.j2
```

**Playbook that uses the role:**

```yaml
---
- hosts: otel_hosts
  become: true
  roles:
    - otel-collector
```

**What this does** вҖ” runs **`roles/otel-collector/tasks/main.yml`** on each **`otel_hosts`** machine. Variables default from **`defaults/main.yml`**, overridden by **`env-vars`** / **`group_vars`** / **`vars/qa`** etc., depending on how **`otel.yml`** is written.

