## 7. OTel collector role вҖ” **`getafix/trunk/ansible/roles/otel-collector`**

Same content as in this repo under **`otel/otel-ansible/roles/otel-collector/`**.

| Piece | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| **`defaults/main.yml`** | Ports (4317 gRPC, 4318 HTTP), memory limits, Jaeger/Prometheus toggles, etc. |
| **`tasks/main.yml`** | Dirs вҶ’ download **`otelcol-contrib`** (S3 or URL) вҶ’ unpack with **`creates=`** вҶ’ **template** config вҶ’ **systemd** вҶ’ enable. |
| **`templates/otel-config.yaml.j2`** | Renders **`/etc/otel/config.yaml`** from variables. |
| **`handlers`** | **Restart** service after config/binary change (once per play). |

**Why Jinja2 (`*.j2`)** вҖ” one template; **qa** vs **prod** only change variables, not duplicate YAML.

**Idempotency**

- **`unarchive`** + **`creates: /usr/local/bin/otelcol-contrib`** вҶ’ skip unpack if binary exists.
- **`template`** + **`validate: 'otelcol-contrib validate --config=%s'`** вҶ’ donвҖҷt write a broken config.

