## 9. Production issues (short stories)

| Symptom | What to check |
|---------|----------------|
| **Playbook changes something every run** | Non-idempotent task; use modules + `creates` / `template`. |
| **SSH fails** | `ansible_host`, user, key, firewall, jump `ProxyCommand`. |
| **Collector didnвҖҷt restart** | **`notify`** / **handler**; task must report **changed**. |
| **OTel not receiving traffic** | 4317/4318, bind address, firewall, TLS vs plain. |
| **Wrong environment** | Wrong **`env-vars`** file, wrong **inventory**, or playbook pointed at **`hosts.qa`** instead of prod. |

